{
  "userId": "USER_ID_HERE"
}

### Remove Member from Team
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/teams/TEAM_ID_HERE/members/USER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### TRAINING SESSIONS
### ============================================

### Get All Trainings
GET {{baseUrl}}/trainings?status=Scheduled&dateFrom=2024-02-01&dateTo=2024-02-28
