### ============================================
### EVENTS
### ============================================

### Get All Events
GET {{baseUrl}}/events?type=Tournament&status=Upcoming
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Event by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/events/EVENT_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create Event
POST {{baseUrl}}/events
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Annual Sports Day",
  "description": "Our biggest event of the year",
  "date": "2024-03-15T00:00:00Z",
  "time": "08:00",
  "type": "Tournament",
  "location": "Main Sports Complex",
  "capacity": 500,
  "status": "Upcoming"
}

### Register for Event
POST {{baseUrl}}/events/EVENT_ID_HERE/participants
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "USER_ID_HERE"
}

### Unregister from Event
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/events/EVENT_ID_HERE/participants/USER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update Participant Result
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/events/EVENT_ID_HERE/participants/USER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "result": "1st Place"
}

